title: ChatMiggle
description: Chatmiggle is a web-based chat application built with Express.js, Socket.io, React, PostgreSQL, Prisma, and Nodemailer. The application is designed to provide real-time chat functionality with a robust backend and modern frontend. 'The entire project is containerized using Docker for ease of deployment and management.
